<![CDATA[
<p>Are you fascinated by human behavior? Psychologists conduct studies to learn what makes people the way they are, including their biology, environment, and culture. The <span class="title-main">Psychology </span>Bachelor of Arts program offers an emphasis in: perception, cognition, and cognitive neuroscience (PCCN); psychobiology; social/personality; developmental.</p>
